#: ../../controlpanel.rst:848
msgid "To view the status of the ZFS pools and the disk(s) in the pool, click the \"ZFS Pools\" tab. In the example, shown in :numref:`Figure %s: Viewing the Status of the ZFS Pool <disk4>`, the ZFS pool named *tank1* was created from one disk. The state of \"Online\" indicates that the pool is healthy."
